      <section eId="sec_CCP-4394">
        <num>CCP 4394</num>
        <heading>4394. Â Service of account</heading>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4394__subsec_1">
          <num>(1)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Upon the undertutor, if an annual account or other interim account is ordered by the court;</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4394__subsec_2">
          <num>(2)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Upon the former minor, if a final account is rendered after expiration of the tutorship; or</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="CCP-4394__subsec_3">
          <num>(3)</num>
          <content>
            <p>Upon the successor tutor, if a final account is rendered after removal, resignation, death, or interdiction of a tutor.</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=111985</p>
        </authorialNote>
      </section>
